Darkness Radio Presents: Supernatural News/Parashare: Skynet Has Already Taken Over Edition!!

After weeks of Tim sitting Bruiser in front of chats and graphs, he might be seeing the light! Well, that and there are, like, seven stories talking about A.I. this week! Also, a man in Brazil puts up Demon statues to impress the neighbors and drive up property values, China throws their space junk at the moon, and Tim reviews the new Foo Fighters Horror/Comedy movie, Studio 666!
